Borges Says EU Officials Working on Bank-Recapitalization Plan

-- B y   R e b e c c a   C h r i s t i e
-- 
2011-10-05T09:55:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-05/borges-says-eu-officials-working-on-bank-recapitalization-plan.html
Antonio Borges, the International
Monetary Fund’s European department head, said European Union
authorities are working together on a plan to recapitalize the
banking sector.  “We would recommend that it move to a European approach,”
Borges said at a press conference in Brussels today. “More
should be done on a cross-border basis.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
Rebecca Christie in Brussels at 
